# Custom Agent Skills

Place your custom skills in this directory. 

A skill can be:
1. A direct root `.md` file (e.g., `.pi/skills/my-skill.md`).
2. A subdirectory containing a `SKILL.md` file (e.g., `.pi/skills/my-skill/SKILL.md`).

## Skill File Structure
```markdown
---
name: my-skill
description: Comprehensive description of when to use this skill.
---
# My Skill Name

## Instructions
List the explicit instructions and workflows the agent should follow when using this skill.
```
